data.description: NEW PRICE! This spacious property features a HUGE living room, 3 beds, 2.5 baths, office, bonus room with walk in closet (could be 4th bedroom), sunroom, & mud room! You'll love the detached garage & 24x22 covered parking pad for your RV & boat. Enjoy the quiet country setting while being close to the amenities of town. Home includes new roof - 4 yrs old, HVAC - 2 yrs old, beautiful bamboo flooring in common areas, new LVP flooring in bedrooms downstairs, & fresh interior & exterior paint.
